body:
last night I dreamt that there was a new Captain America film called 

‘Captain American: Put Some Pants On’

the whole plot of this film was that Steve is depressed and refuses to put pants on so he wonders around for the entire film wearing a half buttoned shirt and his boxers

the only dialogue was Steve’s depressed monologues and the various other Avengers he’s talking to always replying with

‘Cap, put some pants on.’

summary: I'm at a Elizabeth Olsen Panel right now.
body:
I’m at a Elizabeth Olsen Panel right now.

A few things we just learned.

- Her favorite role was in I saw the light.

- Frank Sinatra was her Inspiration to become an actor.

- She would love to do a movie with every other cast member.

- She did not see Captain Marvel yet because she gets anxieties at cinemas.

- She loves football and would love to be on a group chat with the guys.

- She has an obsession with Valkyrie.

- She was asked about Winter Soldier and wondered if people wanted Scarlet Witch and Winter Soldier to be a couple.

title: Marvel Studios’ Avengers: Endgame | Film Clip
body:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZLJ_Mh6qw




Marvel Studios Release New Clip From Avengers Endgame Marvel Studios have released a new clip from its long-awaited Avengers: Endgame and it reveals the most we’ve seen yet about the plot of the Avengers: Infinity War sequel. Adrift in space with no food or water, Tony Stark sends a message to Pepper Potts as his oxygen supply starts to dwindle. Meanwhile, the remaining Avengers – Thor, Black Widow, Captain America and Bruce Banner – must figure out a way to bring back their vanquished allies for an epic showdown with Thanos – the evil demigod who decimated the planet and the universe.

title: Another dream (Post Infinity War)
body:
• The snap didn’t really change Jess’s life much, sure she was pissed about what it meant for people but since she no longer cares for anyone no one she loved was lost. 
  • Work becomes so much lighter though
  • She comes across the other avengers. 
  • Decides she’s going to help out.
  • Her and Barton become an item somehow?? I don’t know how to explain that…all I know is they were together in love deeply and had a kid ALL BEFORE THE UNSNAPPENING.
